<paragraph blockId="55.[151,1436,1871,2042]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1907,1934]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Distribution.</emphasis>
Scattered all over Europe; also North Africa. 
<collectingCountry box="[877,976,1907,1933]" name="Portugal" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: four northern provinces and Ribatejo in this study, and Algarve (Dyte unpubl. data).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="55.[151,1436,1871,2042]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1980,2006]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Ecology.</emphasis>
Recorded equally frequently from forests, parks and riverbanks in 
<collectingCountry box="[1055,1154,1979,2005]" name="Portugal" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Portugal</collectingCountry>
. In northwestern Europe, this species is restricted to saltmarshes and brackish marshes.
</paragraph>
